      "id": "5a93c517_f5491c8c",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/aai/templates/all-services.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 171,
      "message": "They are two ways to register external system to MSB. With this users can call the API with http://IP:PORT/api/aai-externalSystem/v11 or http://IP:PORT/aai/v11/external-system. MSB team recommend us to use the first way (the standard format), but some folks did not familiar with MSB may prefer to use the original API uri. That's why we provide two ways to register service to MSB.",
